<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-20-0979 </DOCNO><TEXT>The ASME Committee on Nuclear Air and Gas Treatment (CONAGT) are at thetime of this writing considering performing maintenance revisions ofANSI N509 and N510 based on the results of a required 5-year review andcomments received from users of the standards at workshops and throughinquiries. This paper discusses the highlights of the significant revisionsto ANSI/ASME N509 and explains the reasons for the changes. It shouldbe emphasized that these revisions are not yet approved by ASME CONAGT,the board of Nuclear Codes and Standards, or ANSI.</TEXT></DOC>